#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
=begin pod
=head2 get-axis-value

Extracts the information from a pad strip or ring event.

=begin code
method get-axis-value ( Array[Int] $index, Num() $value )
=end code

=item $index; (transfer ownership: full) Return location for the axis index.
=item $value; (transfer ownership: full) Return location for the axis value.

=begin comment

