=begin pod
=head2 get-group-mode

Extracts group and mode information from a pad event.

=begin code
method get-group-mode ( Array[Int] $group, Array[Int] $mode )
=end code

=item $group; (transfer ownership: full) return location for the group.
=item $mode; (transfer ownership: full) return location for the mode.

